node.text: Triple H said 😬. This is the smile that made me instantly forget about my blown motor when I get home 😂😍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hertrech Eugene Jr. on July 27, 2021 tagging @jdmcalifornia. May be an image of car.

node.text:
This is the “Simple” part for me. @JDMCalifornia has K24s(and more) on deck for really good prices and you only have to get the @TFWorks K-swap kit once. I didn’t plan on breaking mine so soon but mistakes were made and it is what it is. A normal person would probably take it easy from here but I kind of want to push the limits on this one, lower the rev limit and raise the boost… that should balance everything out right? 😂 Round 2, FIGHT! 
____
Thank you to the homie @fabdaily1986 and @animalauto for making space at their shop for me so we can get this back together with the quickness 🙏🏿

node.text:
Me: 1
K24: 0 
Bad first outing in the Never Getting Seat Time Stallion 😂. The car HATED the altitude change, I pulled up on 10psi(420hp at sea level) and as you can see here it was struggling. Ultimately I think we had the rev limit too high and with the added altitude stress it went kaboom. Thankfully these motors are super cheap, gonna swap it out, lower the rev limiter and beat the life out of it to see if it happens again. Even though my @GridLifeOfficial curse continues it was still an amazing event as usual! Big shout out to the @kseriesparts crew for helping me all weekend 🙏🏿…Until next time 🥲

node.text: Feeling cute, might slam it later 😂. For the first time ever I loaded my car and didn’t crack any aero. Gonna try this “function” thing out for a lil while. On my way to @gridlifeofficial and really hoping I don’t suffer from the new build blues…but even if I do it’s still Grid Life, which is guaranteed good times no matter what. Shout out to my man @otisautoglass for the fresh windshield and @ocmobilealignment for a little bit of straightenin’.

node.text: The current state of my RX7 for Seven’s Day. I popped my 13b a while back, but instead of fixing it and putting it back in the Twerkstallion, @rx7vargas convinced me to start fresh with a 20b and Twerk Jr(my black Turbo II). That’ll be coming soon. Much love to the homies @churchofls for helping me get Twerkstallion sorted with a 6.0 w/ my @garrettmotion GTX4088 strapped to it! I need to take off the rotary exhaust because it’s basically a v8 silencer 😂. But Ole girl made 480hp at 4psi on @igniteracingfuel with a base and will make a perfect yard car for @thehoonigans Tire Slayer Studios.
